        "setup": "For a self-hosted Hasura GraphQL Engine, set an admin secret on the server with the `--admin-secret` flag or `HASURA_GRAPHQL_ADMIN_SECRET` environment variable as documented in [GraphQL Engine Server Configuration Reference](https://hasura.io/docs/2.0/deployment/graphql-engine-flags/reference/) and [Admin Access](https://hasura.io/docs/2.0/auth/authentication/admin-secret-access/). Then use that same secret in client requests as `X-Hasura-Admin-Secret`.",
